and a motorist are dead.

09:12.029 --> 09:13.248
No, no, no.
That wasn't me.

09:13.291 --> 09:14.554
That was the Bondsman.

09:14.597 --> 09:15.729
The who?

09:15.772 --> 09:17.469
Yeah, so,
if you don't kill me

09:17.513 --> 09:18.993
and I don't kill you,

09:19.036 --> 09:21.299
Eccles sends this, uh, demon
they call the Bondsman

09:21.343 --> 09:24.346
to drag me
back to the pit.

09:24.389 --> 09:26.261
And I was hoping
to have a little time

09:26.304 --> 09:28.306
to just hang out.
Ah.

09:28.350 --> 09:30.961
