Is this
too good to be true?

15:46.249 --> 15:47.424
Yeah.

15:48.817 --> 15:51.298
But think about
all the stuff

15:51.341 --> 15:53.648
that was too bad
to be true, huh?

15:53.691 --> 15:54.997
Huh?
Let's -- Let's --

15:55.041 --> 15:57.478
Let's not look a gift horse
in the mouth.

15:57.521 --> 15:59.306
Take it from one
who's had a gift horse --

15:59.349 --> 16:01.351
it doesn't always
work out great.

16:01.395 --> 16:03.614
I'm done.

16:03.658 --> 16:07.705
I'm -- I'm done with
the endless parade of freaks.

16:07.749 --> 16:09.359
Listen to me.

16:09.403 --> 16:10.839
We have
an honest-to-God chance

16:10.882 --> 16:14.234
