Evie:
Heh, that's great.

16:47.658 --> 16:49.095
Listen, I know
this is last-minute,

16:49.138 --> 16:50.618
but does either of you
have any interest

16:50.661 --> 16:52.098
in being a part
of a demonic ritual?

16:52.141 --> 16:53.751
We need
two more for a set.Well --

16:53.795 --> 16:55.231
We're kind of
in the middle

