Just take a minute.

16:56.754 --> 16:57.886
Okay.

16:57.929 --> 16:59.322
Then this
will all be over.

16:59.366 --> 17:01.194
Follow Bill the Demon.

17:01.237 --> 17:02.543
Kevin: Okay.Stan:
Come on, sweetheart.

