no matter what happens,

17:14.859 --> 17:16.078
I just want to say

17:16.122 --> 17:17.558
I really enjoyed
hanging with you guys,

17:17.601 --> 17:19.386
and I'm glad
I didn't kill you.

17:19.429 --> 17:20.822
And I-I-I'd just like
to say --

17:20.865 --> 17:22.389
I don't want to get
too emotional here,

17:22.432 --> 17:23.825
but, brother,
we're all very lucky

17:23.868 --> 17:24.956
